Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:23.29,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界の果てを求め　辿り着く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:27.67,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深い絶望が　溶かしてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:33.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}耐えきれないほどの　憎しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:38.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溢れて流れこむ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:45.53,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}汚れてゆく事は　怖れない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:50.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ためらわずに　Try to dive in now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:56.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Get all the free and dream　君と共に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:01.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明けない夜はないだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:07.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Get all the free and dream　時を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:14.63,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ふたりでひとつのような僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:24.36,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}翼広げ　羽ばたく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:23.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾追尋的世界盡頭  現已在腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:27.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深深絕望  漸漸消解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:33.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}人間憎惡日積月累  終難以承受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:38.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}噴湧而出  流入心胸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:45.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何需畏懼身之污穢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:50.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不再躊躇  Try to dive in now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:56.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Get all the free and dream  只要和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:01.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無光暗夜終將消散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:07.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Get all the free and dream  穿越無盡時空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:14.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}縱使身形相離  只要二人一心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:24.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}張開雙翼  飛向天空
